    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 54-57.</p><p>Legendary AC</p><p>At 20th level, if your AC calculation is lower than your level, you can use your level as your AC instead. If you are using your Legendary AC, you cannot further increase your AC in any way, except by temporary AC increases or magical effects lasting 1 hour or less. Other spells and effects that increase your AC only affect your regular AC.</p><p>Paladin’s AC. Increase your AC by 3. This bonus is increased by 1 when you reach 22nd and 24th level.</p></div>",
